    <h2 style="font-family:'Playfair Display',serif;font-size:1.8rem;color:var(--navy);margin-bottom:1rem;">Baking Trays & Pans</h2>
<img src="/images/bread-slicer.jpg" alt="Bread Slicer" class="product-img" loading="lazy">

    <p style="margin-bottom:1.5rem;">Professional baking trays are the foundation of commercial baking. Commercial trays are made from aluminium, aluminised steel, or stainless steel and are built to withstand daily use in high-temperature ovens. Always buy trays sized to match your oven's interior dimensions.</p>
    <div class="card-grid" style="margin-bottom:3rem;">
      <div class="card"><h3>Aluminium Baking Trays</h3>
<img src="/images/weighing-scale.jpg" alt="Weighing Scale" class="product-img" loading="lazy">
<p>Lightweight, excellent heat distribution, non-reactive. Standard for most commercial bakeries. Available in full, half, and quarter sheet sizes.</p><div class="price-tag">₹180 – ₹650 per tray</div></div>
      <div class="card"><h3>Non-Stick Baking Trays</h3><p>PTFE or silicone-coated trays for products that tend to stick. Essential for cookies, sticky buns, and caramel-topped items.</p><div class="price-tag">₹350 – ₹1,200 per tray</div></div>
      <div class="card"><h3>Perforated Baking Trays</h3><p>Holes in the base allow air circulation for crispier bases — essential for baguettes, rolls, and pizza.</p><div class="price-tag">₹250 – ₹900 per tray</div></div>
      <div class="card"><h3>Silicone Baking Mats</h3><p>Reusable non-stick mats that replace parchment paper. Long-term cost saving for high-volume bakeries.</p><div class="price-tag">₹450 – ₹1,800 per mat</div></div>
    </div>

    <h2 style="font-family:'Playfair Display',serif;font-size:1.8rem;color:var(--navy);margin-bottom:1rem;">Cake Moulds & Baking Rings</h2>
    <div class="card-grid" style="margin-bottom:3rem;">
      <div class="card"><h3>Round Cake Tins</h3><p>Available in 4", 6", 8", 10", 12" diameters. Anodised aluminium for professional bakers; non-stick coating for convenience.</p><div class="price-tag">₹150 – ₹800 per tin</div></div>
      <div class="card"><h3>Loaf Pans / Bread Tins</h3><p>Standard commercial bread loaf pans. Multiple sizes from 400g to 1kg loaf. Aluminised steel for even browning.</p><div class="price-tag">₹120 – ₹450 per pan</div></div>
      <div class="card"><h3>Muffin & Cupcake Trays</h3><p>6-cavity and 12-cavity commercial muffin trays. Non-stick coating essential for easy release.</p><div class="price-tag">₹280 – ₹950 per tray</div></div>
      <div class="card"><h3>Stainless Steel Baking Rings</h3><p>Adjustable rings for entremet cakes and layered desserts. Restaurant-grade finish.</p><div class="price-tag">₹350 – ₹1,500 per set</div></div>
      <div class="card"><h3>Tart & Flan Rings</h3><p>Loose-bottomed tart tins and open rings for professional-quality tarts. Various sizes available.</p><div class="price-tag">₹200 – ₹800</div></div>
      <div class="card"><h3>Silicone Moulds</h3><p>Complex shapes for modern pastry and chocolates. Professional-grade silicone for clean release and food safety compliance.</p><div class="price-tag">₹400 – ₹3,500 per mould</div></div>
    </div>

    <h2 style="font-family:'Playfair Display',serif;font-size:1.8rem;color:var(--navy);margin-bottom:1rem;">Piping, Decorating & Finishing Tools</h2>
    <div class="card-grid" style="margin-bottom:3rem;">
      <div class="card"><h3>Piping Bags</h3><p>Reusable nylon or disposable polythene bags in 10", 12", 14", and 16" sizes. Buy in bulk for commercial use.</p><div class="price-tag">₹25 – ₹80 per bag</div></div>
      <div class="card"><h3>Piping Nozzles / Tips</h3><p>Stainless steel nozzles in star, round, petal, and specialty shapes. A good set is a one-time investment.</p><div class="price-tag">₹15 – ₹250 per nozzle</div></div>
      <div class="card"><h3>Palette Knives / Spatulas</h3><p>Offset and straight palette knives for frosting, spreading ganache, and plating. Flexible stainless steel blades.</p><div class="price-tag">₹120 – ₹450</div></div>
      <div class="card"><h3>Bench Scrapers</h3><p>Stainless steel bench scrapers for portioning dough and cleaning work surfaces. Essential daily-use tool.</p><div class="price-tag">₹80 – ₹250</div></div>
      <div class="card"><h3>Pastry Brushes</h3><p>Natural bristle and silicone pastry brushes for egg wash, butter, and glazes. Silicone is dishwasher safe.</p><div class="price-tag">₹60 – ₹220</div></div>
      <div class="card"><h3>Cake Turntable</h3><p>Aluminium or stainless steel rotating cake stand for professional icing and decorating. Ball-bearing mechanism for smooth rotation.</p><div class="price-tag">₹450 – ₹2,500</div></div>
    </div>

    <h2 style="font-family:'Playfair Display',serif;font-size:1.8rem;color:var(--navy);margin-bottom:1rem;">Weighing Scales & Measuring Tools</h2>
    <p style="margin-bottom:1.5rem;">Precision is everything in baking. Commercial digital scales and accurate measuring tools are non-negotiable for consistent results. For a commercial bakery, invest in reliable, FSSAI-compliant weighing equipment.</p>
    <div class="card-grid" style="margin-bottom:3rem;">
      <div class="card"><h3>Digital Bench Scale (5–15 kg)</h3><p>Accurate to 1g. Essential for weighing flour, sugar, and ingredients. Look for RS232 port for POS integration.</p><div class="price-tag">₹1,800 – ₹8,000</div></div>
      <div class="card"><h3>Precision Scale (0.1g to 3 kg)</h3><p>High-precision scale for small quantities — yeast, salt, spices. 0.1g resolution for accurate recipes.</p><div class="price-tag">₹1,200 – ₹4,500</div></div>
      <div class="card"><h3>Platform Scale (30–150 kg)</h3><p>Large-capacity platform scale for bulk ingredients and heavy deliveries. Essential for stockroom management.</p><div class="price-tag">₹3,500 – ₹15,000</div></div>
    </div>

    <h2 style="font-family:'Playfair Display',serif;font-size:1.8rem;color:var(--navy);margin-bottom:1rem;">Thermometers & Temperature Tools</h2>
    <div class="card-grid" style="margin-bottom:3rem;">
      <div class="card"><h3>Digital Probe Thermometer</h3><p>Instant-read thermometer for checking bread internal temperature, chocolate tempering, and sugar work. Accurate to ±0.5°C.</p><div class="price-tag">₹350 – ₹2,500</div></div>
      <div class="card"><h3>Oven Thermometer</h3><p>Hanging oven thermometer to verify actual oven temperature. Critical for older ovens with unreliable thermostats.</p><div class="price-tag">₹180 – ₹800</div></div>
      <div class="card"><h3>IR / Laser Thermometer</h3><p>Non-contact infrared thermometer for quick surface temperature checks — deck temperature, chocolate work surfaces.</p><div class="price-tag">₹650 – ₹3,000</div></div>
      <div class="card"><h3>Refrigerator Thermometer</h3><p>Monitoring fridge and freezer temperatures. FSSAI compliance requires temperature logging in commercial food storage.</p><div class="price-tag">₹120 – ₹600</div></div>
    </div>

    <h2 style="font-family:'Playfair Display',serif;font-size:1.8rem;color:var(--navy);margin-bottom:1rem;">Bread Proofing & Fermentation Tools</h2>
    <div class="card-grid" style="margin-bottom:2rem;">
