      <div class="card"><h3>Proving / Proofing Cabinet</h3><p>Controlled temperature and humidity cabinet for consistent dough fermentation. Essential for serious artisan bakers.</p><div class="price-tag">₹35,000 – ₹1,20,000</div></div>
      <div class="card"><h3>Bread Lame / Scoring Tool</h3><p>Professional scoring tool for creating decorative patterns and controlled expansion in bread loaves.</p><div class="price-tag">₹120 – ₹450</div></div>
